================================================================================
Bundled engines (each governed by its own LICENSE inside the submodule)
================================================================================

This repository wires several first-party engines as git submodules. Each
submodule ships its own LICENSE file; consult it for the authoritative terms.

  - engines/context-dna           — Context DNA engine (MIT)
                                    https://github.com/supportersimulator/context-dna
  - engines/3-surgeons            — 3-Surgeons multi-model consensus (MIT)
                                    https://github.com/supportersimulator/3-surgeons
  - engines/multi-fleet           — Multi-Fleet transport (MIT)
                                    https://github.com/supportersimulator/multi-fleet
  - apps/ide-shell                — Admin / IDE Shell panel substrate (MIT)
                                    https://github.com/supportersimulator/admin.contextdna.io

The bootstrap script (scripts/bootstrap-from-scratch.sh) clones these submodules
verbatim. Their copyright notices remain with their respective authors.


